item.title: The Einstein Show - May 28, 2013
item.description: Hour 1 - Dylan and Liza tell about the slumber party then went to on Friday. Sarah and Lisa join them on the phone. Also includes Loliwood shout-outs. Hour 2 - A game of 'Strip Poker' between some girls from rival schools. Hour 3 - Longtime Playdate model Michelle Wallace stops in and tells us some of the stories from her work in the magazine.
